This is an IRC Translation Bot. 
I made it for English / Spanish / Portuguese translations. 

It relies on Google Translate. 

The code is GPLv3. Feel free to modify as you see fit. 

Usage:
!translate [text to translate]
Translates any language, to english

!traducir [text to translate]
Translates any language, to spanish

!traduzir [text to translate]
Translates any language, to portuguese. 

!monitor #irc-channel language_you_dont_speak language_you_speak
Usage for langauge: en, es, pt. 

!demonitor #irc-channel language_you_dont_speak
Removes room monitoring. 
